<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>mesh</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>- mesh with holes </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>holeRepresentativeEdges</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>- each edge here represents a hole borders that should be filled should be not empty edges should have invalid left face (FaceId == -1) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
